# Booster

A set of tools for creating application-like RoboFont extensions.

Most of the functionality comes from subclassing two main classes:


```python
BoosterController
    .owner
    .fontWrapperClass
    .documentClass

    .teardown()

    # Defaults
    .userDefaults
    .registerUserDefaults()
    .getUserDefault()
    .setUserDefault()

    # Menubar
    .menubar
    .buildMenu()
    .getMenuItemData()
    .setMenuItemData()

    # Notifications
    .addObserver()
    .removeObserver()
    .postNotification()

    # Requests
    .addResponder()
    .removeResponder()
    .postRequest()

    # Fonts
    .getAllFonts()
    .openFont()
    .getCurrentFont()

    # Documents
    .newDocument()
    .closeDocument()

BoosterDocument

    .documentController

    # Notifications
    .addObserver()
    .removeObserver()
    .postNotification()

    # Requests
    .addResponder()
    .removeResponder()
    .postRequest()
```

This high-level API is a convenience wrapper around a set of low-level APIs.

```python
    environment
        identifier
        inRoboFont
    menubar
        SharedMenubar()
            .buildMenu()
            .teardownMenu()
            .getItem()
            .getItemData()
            .setItemData()
    notifications
        SharedNotificationCenter()
            --- very ugly. needs to be cleaned up.
    requests
        SharedRequestCenter()
            .addResponder()
            .removeResponder()
            .postRequest()
    defaults
        SharedUserDefaults()
            .registerDefaults()
            .getDefault()
            .setDefault()
    objects
            AllFonts()
            CurrentFont()
            CurrentGlyph()
            NewFont()
            OpenFont()
            class AppExtBase
                .getRepresentation()
                .destroyRepresentation()
                .destroyAllRepresentations()
                .addObserver()
                .removeObserver()
                .hasObserver()
                .holdNotifications()
                .releaseHeldNotifications()
                .disableNotifications()
                .enableNotifications()
                .postNotification()
            class AppExtFont
            class AppExtInfo
            class AppExtGroups
            class AppExtKerning
            class AppExtFeatures
            class AppExtLib
            class AppExtLayer
            class AppExtGlyph
            class AppExtContour
            class AppExtComponent
            class AppExtAnchor
            class AppExtGuideline
            class AppExtImage
    activity
        SharedActivityCenter()
            .addObserver()
            .removeObserver()
            .getActivity()
boosterUI
    settings
        - activity
```